fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtktreeview-h.html#gtk_tree_view_scroll_to_point", "fragment": "Gtk.TreeView.ScrollToPoint \nScrolls the tree view such that the top left corner of the visible area is tree_x tree_y where tree_x and tree_y are specified in tree coordinates. The tree_view must be realized before this function is called. If it isn t you probably want to be using Gtk.TreeView.ScrollToCell. \nIf either tree_x or tree_y are then that direction isn t scrolled. \nParameters \nX coordinate of new top left pixel of visible area or \nY coordinate of new top left pixel of visible area or \n"});